  <brief_title>Treatment of Late Abortion: Evacuatio Uteri or Conservative Treatment</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evacuatio Uteri or Conservtive Treatment After Late Abortion. A Randomize Trial.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
